 "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/gaming/480729/fields-of-mistria-first-big-patch-notes-romance", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "New major Fields of Mistria patch out now, adds romance and animal mounts", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-18T15:10:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/Titan-A-badge-sq.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,89.4\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/star-trek\">Star Trek</a> franchise is a flexible one, in which the best Trek series find time to be both serious and silly, to host <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/23768513/star-trek-strange-new-worlds-episode-season-2-oona-pike\">trial episodes</a>, action-adventure, <a href=\"https://memory-alpha.fandom.com/wiki/Memento_Mori_(episode)\">submarine thrillers</a>, and even the occasional mystery (with or without Data dressed up as Sherlock Holmes).\u00a0</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Maybe that\u2019s what makes Beadle &amp; Grimm\u2019s latest <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/beadleandgrimms/star-trek-murder-mystery-escape-r", "id": 1538717, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/tabletop-games/478894/star-trek-murder-mystery-box-beadle-grimm", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https: