te_published": "2024-11-18T14:00:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Jinx wearing a hood and looking out from under it in a still from Arcane season 2\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Riot Games, Fortiche/Netflix\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/Arcane_u_S2_00_01_49_21_R.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Let\u2019s be honest: This is a little bit of a fake week, if you\u2019re in the U.S. Many folks are still smarting from the election, while also stuck making plans (food, travel, or otherwise) for Thanksgiving next week, and maybe even recovering from Daylight Savings a few weeks ago. What are we left to do with our time while we winnow down the increasingly little daylight hours? </p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">As ever, my advice is: watch TV! Why not? There are so many good options going around these days as we barrel towards the end of the ye", "id": 1538262, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/tv/477994/new-netflix-tv-arcane-finale-when-franchise-interior-chinatown-based-true-story", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Netflix\u2019s Arcane series finale, Interior: Chinatown, and more new TV this week", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-18T13:13:20+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/game_awards_2024_logo.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Geoff Keighley\u2019s The Game Awards celebrates its 10th anniversary in 2024. The annual awards show and video game trailer extravaganza returns on Thursday, Dec. 12 for a night that aims to celebrate the year\u2019s best and biggest games, while giving viewers sneak peeks of games to come. </p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">On Monday, organizers revealed the <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/480312/game-awards-2024-nominees-list-game-of-the-year\">nominees for 2024\u2019s The Game Awards</a>, with <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/review/447564/astro-bot-review\">Astro Bot</a></em>, <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/review/461096/metaphor-refantazio-review-ps5-ps4-xb", "id": 1537792, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/events/479292/game-awards-2024-start-time-nominees", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "How to watch The Game Awards 2024", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-18T13:03:17+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A graphic showing images from Dragon Age: The Veilguard, Astro Bot, Metaphor: ReFantazio, Final Fantasy 7 Rebirth, and Balatro\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/goty-frontrunners-v3.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap has-text-align-none\">This year marks the 10th anniversary of The Game Awards, and in that time Geoff Keighley\u2019s annual event has established itself quite firmly as the leading awards ceremony for the game industry \u2014 the Oscars of gaming. It remains promotionally overstuffed to the point that it\u2019s still arguably better known for trailers than awards, but that\u2019s changing. And although its winners tend to be pretty conservative, they are broadly representative of the critical consensus. Its voting body is composed of a wide range of international ", "id": 1537793, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/awards/450195/game-of-the-year-game-awards-frontrunners", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Game of the Year: Which of the 2024 Game Award nominees will win?", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-18T12:58:20+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Square Enix via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25482093/ffxiv_dx11_2024_06_07_13_41_04.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>Allied society quests</strong> are one of <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/ffxiv-guides-ff14-final-fantasy-14-online/22381941/beginners-job-subscription-teleport-mount-shadowbringers-endwalker\"><em>Final Fantasy 14</em></a>\u2019s more rewarding <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/ffxiv-guides-ff14-final-fantasy-14-online/24118981/reset-daily-weekly-times-server-time\">dailies</a>. Formerly known as \u201cbeast tribe quests\u201d or \u201ctribal quests,\u201d these quests involving helping out the other races of Eorzea by beating down baddies that might be giving them grief, or helping them rebuild an area using crafting and gathering.", "id": 1537794, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/ffxiv-guides-ff14-final-fantasy-14-online/480866/allied-society-quests-ranks-mounts-tribes", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Where to unlock all allied society quests in FFXIV", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-18T12:16:03+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/game_awards_2024_logo.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The Game Awards announced its nominees for Game of the Year 2024 in a livestream Monday. <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/awards/450195/game-of-the-year-game-awards-frontrunners\">This year\u2019s race for GOTY hasn\u2019t had an obvious frontrunner</a> thus far, making the announcement one of the bigger surprises in the show\u2019s 10-year history.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">As of today\u2019s announcement, the six nominees for Game of the Year are locked in, which kicks off the second stage of jury voting. The jury will also select from nominees for categories like Best Mobile Game, Best Debut Indie Game, and more. We will keep this post updated with nominees for other", "id": 1537345, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/480312/game-awards-2024-nominees-list-game-of-the-year", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "The Game Awards announces Game of the Year 2024 nominees", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-11-18T11:10:57+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/11/chrome_2024-11-15_13-59-39.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/genshin-impact/40711\">Genshin Impact</a></em>\u2019s 5.2 patch is coming soon, bringing new characters and story with it. This patch will conclude the Natlan archon quest, as well as introduce the two new playable characters, Chasca and Ororon.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Below, we explain when <em>Genshin Impact </em>maintenance starts and ends, alongside the release time of patch 5.2. We\u2019ve also added some details about what to expect from <em>Genshin Impact</em> version 5.2.</p>\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\" />\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What time does Genshin Impact go down f", "id": 1536863, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/genshin-impact-guides/480064/version-5-2-release-times-maintenance-end", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "What time does Genshin